Anonymous Fri 28 Jun 2024 23:59:07 No.66981679 Report
Quoted By: >>66981714
>>66981368
Extinction would be nicer.
That's the worst part.

CWD has been around for a long time but recently there's been a change. Maybe a slightly different form of the prion.

Many prion diseases we've seen before are limited in where the affected proteins appear. There was one that was shared among cannibals on an island. They ate the brain of their deceased in a ritual, and that transmitted the prion. Stop eating prion brains, the disease burned out.

But CWD prion appears in all fluids. A CWD deer rubs noses with a clean deer, doomed. Passes the placenta, too. Mom's doomed? Fawn's doomed.

It lasts for years in the soil, it can be carried by birds to new populations, and
>>66981440
it's jumping species to other mammals.
>>66981483
Recently two hunters who didn't give a fuck and took from known CWD herds got the rot.

One molecule gets in your fluids, set the timer for two years because you're done.
